{
  "chapter": 31,
  "chapter_summary": "仇恕向端木方正、石磷解释自己不能放过毛臬：毛臬虽败，仍可能借未现身的十大使者和巨万家财暗组势力。石磷担心仇恕现身后旧仇缠身，提出以“还魂”面具制造身外化身。慕容惜生戴面具闯入追问毛文琪下落，四名“还魂”混战换位，反使众人错认。慕容惜生算准仇恕心理先行引走他，端木方正与石磷误斗后才知中计。仇恕又将慕容惜生误作端木方正，出言讥其容貌，被她扣脉点穴擒住，只得谎称能寻找毛文琪，被迫同行。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "酒窖已被小弟用做牢房，此刻已拿不出酒来了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "小弟岂是真的要酒，只不过是要逼你说出这句话来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "程潘两位前辈，与仇兄渊源非浅，仇兄为何要将他两人灌醉后困在地牢里？\n\n实令小弟难解！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "小弟怎地什么事都瞒不过兄台……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "只因我那两位叔父，一心要劝我化解冤仇，是以……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "冤仇能解，有何不好？令堂大人，必定也高兴得很。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "仇兄，你我虽属初交，却是一见如故，小弟有几句肺腑之忠言，不知仇兄可愿一听？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "兄台若是不说，小弟必将遗憾终生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "常言道杀人不过头点地，那毛臬与仇兄虽有不共戴天之仇，但他却又是仇兄的至亲舅父。\n\n何况，他爱女亦与仇兄有一段感情，这期间恩怨纠缠，虽非我等外人所能了解，但……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "得饶人处且饶人，仇兄你既然已将他逼得众叛亲离，无家可归，你何不就从此放他一条生路？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "这其间确是恩怨纠缠，连小弟自己也难以化解，但……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "但兄台若说毛臬此刻已至末路，小弟却绝不赞成！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "他不但在杭州城中无法立足，在武林中也失去了人心，他武功虽仍在，但从此以后，已与人无害，更不能影响别人，最多也不过只能寻个隐避之处，寂寞地度过晚年而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "以毛臬那样桀骜不驯的人物，怎甘寂寂终老？\n\n他杭州城的基业虽毁，但百足之虫，死而不僵，何况他远在'杭州英雄大会'成败未知前，便早已布置好退路，准备日后东山再起，到那时再要除他，便绝非易事了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "何以见得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "兄台可曾发现，毛臬的十大玉骨使者，在'杭州英雄大会'中俱未现身，'七星鞭'杜仲奇与他交情最厚，但直到此刻，也未见踪影，此事若不注意，便难发现，一经发现，便可看出其中正有无穷巧妙！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "灵蛇十大弟子，仿佛已死了多人……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "虽已死了多人，但还有夺命使者铁平，银刀使者欧阳明，'铁军使者'长孙策……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "这三人在十大弟子中已属佼佼人物，更何况十大使者为首的一人'铁胆使者'钱卓亦从未现身！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "七剑三鞭，都已瓦解，十大使者，又有何可怕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "可怕的并非这十大使者，而是怕他们在暗中收买江湖中的败类，组织成一种秘密的势力，常言道明枪易躲，暗箭难防，'灵蛇'此番失败，只因他太过招摇，此人若是又在暗中成了气候，你我都未见得是他的敌手了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "仇兄剖析精微，小弟佩服……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "毛臬称霸江湖多年，黑白两道的生意，他都要插上一足，二十年来他积下的家财，必定已是个惊人的数字，但他的家在火焚之后，其中却并无金钱，那么他的巨万家财，又到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "莫非已被他用做暗中搜集党羽的基金？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "若事情真被我等料中，此人便当真可算是个枭雄之才，地上创业不终，立刻转入地下……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是以小弟无论是为了私仇抑或公益，都不能就此罢手，两位此刻听了小弟的这一番言语，便该体谅小弟的苦衷了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "但另有一事，你却要多加注意。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_shi_lin",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你爹爹昔日在江湖中曾结下无数仇家，如今你一现出真面目来，要寻你复仇的人，便太多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_shi_lin",
      "text": "这个我……我已知道。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你既要寻人复仇，又要防人复仇，而你的势力，却又如此孤单，你的脾气，却又如此强傲……唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自从九足神蛛去后，我已算势力孤单，但直到此刻，我又发觉了我到底还有几个真正的朋友！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "穷家帮凌龙帮主无论武功、声望，俱是江湖中一流人物，而且此老为人热肠，你为何不求他相助？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "此老曾与我言语冲突，只怕日后再也不会予我援手了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖中人此刻都只道毛臬众叛亲离，已至穷途末路，又有谁知道我势力的孤单，更在毛臬之上。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你可知道我怎会戴了这面具来见你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "无论你如何猜法，都猜不到的，我与端木兄相识以来，一直心灰意冷，更不愿再过问江湖中事，那日见到他做了个这样的面具，一时兴起，也学着戴了起来，只因这面具仿制甚是容易，短短几日我便制了许多……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_shi_lin",
      "text": "你可是要我也戴上这种面具？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "神话传奇中，常有'身外化身'之说，你我若也邀集些朋友，俱都戴上这种面具，那时又有谁会知道哪一个'还魂'是端木方正，哪一个'还魂'是仇恕，你岂非也有了许多'身外化身'了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_shi_lin",
      "text": "若是有别的武林中人，也一齐来仿制这种面具，用来为非作歹，到那时你我又该当如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "这个你倒毋庸过虑，制作这种面具，石兄说来虽易，其实却绝非易事，只因它制作虽易，但知道这制作方法之人，世上却廖廖无几，即使别人也制作了这'还魂'面具戴上，反可淆乱别人的耳目，此事说来虽不甚光明，但用来对付毛臬这般人物，正是以其人之道，还治其人之身！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此举用来对付毛臬则可，但小弟却不愿以此来逃避先父的仇家，只因小弟此番出道江湖，便是为了要了清先人的恩仇！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "无论如何，我且送一具给你，用与不用，便全由得你了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有人拍门！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去应门！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "外面难道没有人么？拍门的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "拍门的便是我！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "慕容惜生，你又来作甚？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "不错，我就是慕容惜生，我只来问你，你将我师妹逼到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "我要知道她去了何处，此刻我便早已追去了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
