    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "这里还有个'还魂'，你认得我么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "姓仇的，你莫来弄这个玄虚，我只要你还我的师妹来，否则我便要叫你回去在家师面前交代！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "谁陪你回去，谁是姓仇的，我也是还魂，你可要看清了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_shi_lin",
      "text": "石磷！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "你……难道是端木兄？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_shi_lin",
      "text": "错了，错了，你我全都错了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_shi_lin",
      "text": "这就叫作法自毙，我两人一心想帮仇恕引开慕容惜生，哪知竟帮了倒忙，反帮了慕容惜生了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "仇恕若将慕容惜生当作了我们，那后果岂非不堪设想？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_shi_lin",
      "text": "追！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_lin",
      "speaker_name": "石磷",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "只怕是追不上了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_shi_lin",
      "text": "追不上也要追的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "端木兄，等我一等！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "方才幸好只有四个还魂，否则小弟也要糊涂了，端木兄，那慕容惜生确非普通女子，只可惜容颜太恶，否则倒真是才貌双全，难得得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "端木兄，那边是什么方向？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我便是容颜太恶的慕容惜生。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "慕容姑娘，你可知道男女授受不亲，你如此拉着我的手腕，岂非失礼得很，嘿嘿，失礼得很！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你若不愿我拉你的手腕，我便点上你的\"晕穴\"也可以，这两条路任你选择，我绝不勉强。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "无妨无妨，就这样好了！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我也懒得背着你走，但你脚下却不可偷懒！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "慕容姑娘，你究竟是要在下陪你去回去见令师呢，还是要在下陪你见令师妹毛姑娘？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你知不知道我师妹在哪里？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "在下此刻虽不知道，但找是必定找得到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你可有把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "自有把握，慕容姑娘若不相信，在下……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "既有把握，我便随你去找，道路也任你选择，但你若找不到时……哼哼，你可知道我容颜虽恶，却还不及我手段之恶呢！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你切切不可妄生脱逃之心，我辛辛苦苦擒住了你，便万万不会放你逃走，我睡时要点你晕穴，醒时便扣住你手腕，你若要乱玩花样，我便断去你左足，替你配上木腿，反正我容颜丑恶，也不需避什么男女之嫌！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "哪里走？快走……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    }
